snippet: WebMD says it has taken itself off the auction block, after failing to attract satisfactory offers from potential buyers.
abstract: WebMD says it has taken itself off the auction block, after failing to attract satisfactory offers from potential buyers.

byline.original: By MICHAEL J. DE LA MERCED

lead_paragraph: The online health company WebMD said on Tuesday that it had taken itself off the auction block, after failing to attract satisfactory offers from potential buyers.
